import React, { Component } from 'react';

class New extends Component {

    render(){
        
        return(

            <form id="new-post">

                <input 
                
                    type="file" 
                />

                <input 

                    type="text"
                    name="author"
                    placeholder="Autor do post"
                />

                <input 

                    type="text"
                    name="place"
                    placeholder="Local do post"
                />

                <input 

                    type="text"
                    name="description"
                    placeholder="Descrição do post"
                />

                <input 

                    type="text"
                    name="hashtags"
                    placeholder="Hashtags do post"
                />

            </form>
        )
    }
}

export default New;
